summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 6004 for the improvement of The Alley between Blocks 3 and 4, Central Park Addition to West Seattle, being the alley between 44th Avenue Southwest and 45th Avenue Southwest from West Alaskan Street to West Edmunds Street, and certain other streets, avenues and alleys, by paving and otherwise improving the same, under Ordinance No. 80639, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, and establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
